org.openhab.binding.velux.internal - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal
Classes for handling of openHAB bindings and configurations.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge
Classes for Generic protocol-independent interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices via the Velux gateway.

Interface definitions being used to implement the protocol-dependent interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.

JSON-protocol specific implementations of the interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.slip - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.slip
SLIP-protocol specific implementations of the interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.slip.io - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.slip.io

Utility classes for the SLIP-protocol.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.config - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.config
Class with default openHAB configuration definitions.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.development - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.development
Generic classes to support development of bindings.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.discovery - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.discovery
Classes to provide the discovery of things automatically and user-initiated after defining a valid Velux bridge configuration.

Classes to provide the initiation of all handlers i.e. the factory for all services and things.

Classes for handling any kind of openHAB events and requests, providing a synchronisation between openHAB and the real world.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.handler.utils - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.handler.utils
Helper classes for dealing with configurations, properties, things and channels.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things
Classes for modeling the Velux devices and their properties in a general openHAB (OH1/OH2/OH3)-independent way.
org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.utils - package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.utils
Generic utility classes (might not be limited to the Velux binding).
